      <title>特朗普加征关税后，美国炼油商将目光投向拉丁美洲和伊拉克</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-oil-refiners-look-to-latin-america-iraq-after-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易商表示，在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普采取关税措施后，美国炼油商将把目光投向拉丁美洲和中东，以取代突然上涨的加拿大和墨西哥原油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-oil-refiners-look-to-latin-america-iraq-after-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:58:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞穗银行实现创纪录目标，利润超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mizuho-profit-beats-estimates-as-bank-achieves-record-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞穗金融集团第三季度利润上涨，由于利率上升推动贷款收入增加，其提前超越了创纪录的年度盈利预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mizuho-profit-beats-estimates-as-bank-achieves-record-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:44:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧莱雅向制药商回售 30 亿欧元赛诺菲股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/l-oreal-to-sell-3-billion-of-sanofi-shares-back-to-drugmaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[化妆品巨头欧莱雅公司 (L’Oreal SA) 正将所持价值 30 亿欧元（31 亿美元）的赛诺菲股份出售给这家法国制药商，在赛诺菲股价过去一年跑赢大盘后，欧莱雅将部分持股变现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/l-oreal-to-sell-3-billion-of-sanofi-shares-back-to-drugmaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:43:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>滞胀风险导致美国国债收益率曲线自 11 月以来最趋平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对主要贸易伙伴加征关税的举动可能导致经济陷入滞胀，美国国债收益率曲线创下 11 周以来的最大平缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税引发通胀和经济增长担忧，金属价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收关税，威胁爆发可能削弱全球经济增长的贸易战，铜、铝和铁矿石领跌金属价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普考虑下一轮关税，欧洲股指期货下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/european-stock-futures-slide-as-trump-eyes-next-round-of-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡该地区成为下一个受到美国关税影响的国家的可能性，欧洲股指期货暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/european-stock-futures-slide-as-trump-eyes-next-round-of-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:53:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强抵消避险需求，黄金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对来自加拿大、墨西哥和中国的进口商品征收关税后，金价下跌，因为在全球准备应对贸易战的情况下，美元飙升超过了避险需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普征收关税导致美元飙升，股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普兑现对加拿大、墨西哥和中国进口产品征收关税的威胁后，美元飙升，而股票市场和数字货币暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度回应特朗普 力图摆脱“关税之王”称号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/shun-protectionism-india-signals-to-industry-with-tariff-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府在预算中大幅削减了进口关税，并表示不会利用保护主义措施来庇护企业，这显然是为了阻止美国总统唐纳德·特朗普与其主要合作伙伴发动新一轮贸易战的报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/shun-protectionism-india-signals-to-industry-with-tariff-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 12:16:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
